Dear Divanshu, 

I hereby agree to the above mentioned terms and conditions stated by
you. Kindly find the following Job description. 

Business development Executive(Male):-

The BDE will be the face of the company and will carry out meetings with
the prospective clients and explaining them about our product/services.
He should possess good communication skills and convincing power. He
should be well versed with basic computer skills and should have
knowledge of internet and latest technologies. Language proficiency in
English is must.Candidates having their own two wheeler will be given
preference.

Salary:- 1,20,000 - 1,50,000 Lpa
Qualification:- Any graduate
Allowances:- Daily Travelling Allowance + Incentive.
Location:- Sector-10,Noida 

Tele-caller(Female) Business Development:-

The tele-caller will reach out to all the prospective clients over call,
She should have good communication skills and good command over English.
She should have convincing skills to encourage prospective service
providers to sign up with us. This is a office based job and doesn't
require travelling .

Salary :- 1,00,000-1,20,000 lpa
Qualification :- Any Graduate
Location :- Sector-10, Noida

Company Address:- A-7,1st Floor, Manhattan Building,Sector-10,
Noida-201301.
Website :- www.simplifytrips.com [1]
Contact Number:- 7567949606, 8890780236
Contact Person:- Tushar Choudhary.

For any queries, do revert.

